{"title":"Endometriosis iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Obstetricia y Ginecología/Endometriosis iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Endometriosis","guid":"gQtyu0vkrrcr5wAr2zflQQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición y\\NEpidemiología","guid":"iLVKq_-6ggpTxb8BroRqZA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Tejido endometrial ectópico → inflamación crónica estrógeno-dependiente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Prevalencia 5-10% mujeres en edad reproductiva (~190 millones mundial)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Retraso diagnóstico promedio 6-10 AÑOS desde síntomas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"COEXISTENCIA con adenomiosis ~50% casos → mismo espectro patogénico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Teorías\\Nprincipales","guid":"LDvNyOHgzoG0kPBJ91tVVg","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Implantación retrógrada (Sampson) → más aceptada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Metaplasia celómica → explica sitios extraperitoneales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"Diseminación hematógena/linfática → lesiones distantes (pulmón, SNC)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"6","text":"Mecanismos\\Nmoleculares","guid":"r-nG4NHWEGKtIhn_k9Ukrw","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"RESISTENCIA a progesterona → falla apoptosis células ectópicas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"↑ Aromatasa local → producción estrógenos in situ → autocrina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"Inflamación crónica → IL-1, IL-6, TNF-α, VEGF ↑","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"11","text":"Angiogénesis aberrante → vascularización lesiones","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"6","text":"Adenomiosis vs\\NEndometriosis profunda","guid":"HHEaFLEKYlb9893QKzS07A","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Mismo origen embriológico probable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"Fenotipos diferenciales del mismo proceso estrógeno-dependiente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"Donnez J, Best Pract Res Clin Obstet Gynaecol 2023","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"rASRM (revisada\\NSociedad Americana\\NMedicina Reproductiva)","guid":"5Cx5h0X_S8clrNcSBYgYww","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Estadio I-II → enfermedad mínima/leve","guid":"","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"DIFÍCIL diagnóstico no quirúrgico → sin marcadores validados","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Estadio III → moderada (adherencias, endometriomas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Estadio IV → severa (obliteración fondo de saco Douglas)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"20","text":"Endometriosis\\Nprofunda\\N(DIE)","guid":"CS-ljAjUlQCnt9ScJiWkQQ","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Infiltración >5mm bajo peritoneo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Nódulos rectovaginales, ureterales, vesicales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"Mayor correlación síntomas/severidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"20","text":"Endometrioma\\Novárico","guid":"Aj4KWM9jOrB-IjRGkoJHVA","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Quiste ovárico con revestimiento endometrial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"Recurrencia a 24 meses post-cirugía SIN hormonoterapia → 27%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"Veth VB, Fertil Steril 2024","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"Presentación\\NClínica","guid":"bY-AEvgh83U_wM0fcDi_5A","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"Síntomas\\Ncardinales\\N(4D)","guid":"AY7vmiWPjA7ajBhuJb1IgA","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"DISMENORREA → inicio cólico menstrual progresivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"DISPAREUNIA → profunda, poscoital","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"DISQUECIA → dolor defecación (↑ período menstrual)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"DISURIA → lesión vesical/ureteral","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"34","text":"Dolor pélvico\\Ncrónico","guid":"7zM62MFEZFAa9xPtRyuJ1Q","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Mecanismo mixto: inflamatorio + neuropático + central","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Sensibilización central → amplificación dolor","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"34","text":"Infertilidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"30-50% mujeres con endometriosis tienen infertilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Mecanismos: obstrucción tubárica, toxicidad folicular, implantación alterada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"34","text":"Manifestaciones\\Nextragenitales","guid":"1AxD4NOvLRo6SrnEcmDC6w","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Catamenial: neumotórax, hemoptisis (endometriosis torácica rara)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Ciatalgia menstrual → nódulo ciático","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"34","text":"Salud\\Nmental","guid":"wieRbzH5m85T3se2-22GgA","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"↑ Depresión y ansiedad vs. población general","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"Disfunción sexual → impacto calidad de vida severo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"Predisposición genética compartida dolor-trastorno afectivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"49","text":"Zippl AL, Fertil Steril 2023","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Clínico\\Nprimero","guid":"3xiOgkdnxJqhqQuXc4Iihg","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Síntomas + historia menstrual + examen pélvico orientan fuertemente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial: SII, EPI, quiste ovárico funcional","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"Imágenes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"ECOGRAFÍA TRANSVAGINAL\\N→ primera línea","guid":"qR9J8uNK96tIMToyU-KnhA","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Endometriomas → imagen en vidrio esmerilado, alta S/E","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"DIE → requiere operador experto (protocolo IDEA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"59","text":"Estadios I-II → baja sensibilidad ecográfica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"58","text":"RMN pelvis → alternativa/complemento DIE","guid":"JpB6g2YTkqZN65FGMPHYdw","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"Mejor para plano rectovaginal y lesiones vesicales","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"54","text":"Biomarcadores\\N(no validados clínicamente aún)","guid":"nmmlvQweOo81yW0oTZw1IQ","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"CA-125 → baja especificidad (↑ otras condiciones)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"miRNA séricos → investigación activa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"BCL6 endometrial → asociación prometedora Estadio I-II","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"Young SL, Fertil Steril 2023","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"54","text":"LAPAROSCOPIA + BIOPSIA \\N→ gold standard histológico","guid":"nvYUssMljL6mgCNNd9Jnfg","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Requerida para Estadios I-II con diagnóstico incierto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"Permite diagnóstico Y tratamiento simultáneo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"Principios\\Ngenerales","guid":"g1OoaLP8ri1Kf9eig54ZSw","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"Enfoque MULTIMODAL → dolor + fertilidad + salud mental","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"Tratamiento individualizado según: edad, deseo reproductivo, severidad, síntomas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"No cura → control de enfermedad crónica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"Manejo\\Ndel Dolor","guid":"VeCN_7FTKeAgn1HWcNLnzw","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"AINEs → primera línea analgesia aguda","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"Ibuprofeno/naproxeno → preferir inicio menstrual","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"Hormonoterapia \\N→ supresión estrogénica","guid":"ZX2xaSORge3AjQgkrrnl-A","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"Anticonceptivos combinados (ACO) → primera línea largo plazo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"Progestágenos solos → dienogest, medroxiprogesterona","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"Análogos GnRH → segunda línea, máx 6 meses sin add-back","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Add-back estrógenos/progestágeno → previene pérdida ósea","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"81","text":"DIU levonorgestrel → especialmente dismenorrea/adenomiosis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"78","text":"Enfoque multimodal\\Ndolor neuropático","guid":"YISltmod-FVFF7OhL7iJAQ","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"Amitriptilina, duloxetina, gabapentinoides → adjuvantes","guid":"ifq5hg3CuGXOEzlIkQ9_OQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"Derivación Psicología → CBT, mindfulness","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"73","text":"Manejo\\NFertilidad","guid":"y9K2Zio4ZtHf7tkfTv1evQ","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Hormonoterapia NO mejora fertilidad → suspender para intentar concepción","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"Estadios I-II + infertilidad → LAPAROSCOPIA mejora tasas embarazo espontáneo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"Endometrioma → cistectomía laparoscópica mejora acceso folicular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"Endometriosis severa + infertilidad → FIV/ICSI","guid":"","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"Tasas similares a otras causas infertilidad si endometrio receptivo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"73","text":"Cirugía","guid":"","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Laparoscopia conservadora → resección lesiones + preservación ovario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"Cirugía radical → histerectomía ± ooforectomía → última opción","guid":"","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"Solo si completado deseo reproductivo + refractaria a tto médico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"96","text":"RECURRENCIA post-cirugía\\NSIN hormonoterapia:","guid":"Jrgg9YqZjLCoJRKlksTGhQ","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"3 meses → 4% | 6 meses → 14% | 12 meses → 17% | 24 meses → 27%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"→ Hormonoterapia post-cirugía RECOMENDADA para prevenir recurrencia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"96","text":"Veth VB, Fertil Steril 2024","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"73","text":"Tratamiento\\Nsalud mental","guid":"stCH8XFNJfLQP7sdjLsW7w","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"Tamizaje sistemático depresión/ansiedad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"Intervención multidisciplinaria → ginecólogo + psicólogo + fisioterapeuta pélvico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y\\NPronóstico","guid":"dX7NkdlMvaQiI4HPzYB1xg","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"Enfermedad RECURRENTE y CRÓNICA → seguimiento de por vida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"Riesgo de recurrencia ↑ sin supresión hormonal post-cirugía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"Transición menopausia → síntomas pueden mejorar espontáneamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"107","text":"Riesgo leve ↑ carcinoma endometrioide/células claras ovárico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"107","text":"Control dolor + fertilidad + calidad de vida → objetivos principales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NEspeciales","guid":"tIHhxhKaMgTdnQTOciqprg","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"Endometriosis\\Ny embarazo","guid":"H2H6TycmEVnSuPtZPIVbqQ","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"Puede MEJORAR temporalmente durante gestación (efecto progestágeno)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"↑ Riesgo: placenta previa, parto prematuro, cesárea","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"Impacto\\Nsocioeconómico","guid":"_ovOt4Xp1JNU1f6n3ietaw","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"Pérdida productividad, ausentismo laboral significativo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"Costo estimado ~10.000 USD/paciente/año (EE.UU.)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"113","text":"Investigación\\Nactiva","guid":"64BmOHbg_3-C3OU2_RMieg","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"Biomarcadores no invasivos → prioridad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"Terapias no hormonales → antiangiogénicos, inmunomoduladores","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"ABtzYNPqfFw41S6Jr2mEgQ","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"Retraso diagnóstico promedio 7 años → preguntar activamente dismenorrea progresiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"CA-125 NO sirve para diagnóstico → solo seguimiento en casos seleccionados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"123","text":"Hormonoterapia post-cirugía OBLIGATORIA para reducir recurrencia (27% a 2 años sin ella)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"123","text":"Análogos GnRH >6 meses sin add-back → pérdida ósea irreversible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"123","text":"Estadios I-II → ecografía normal NO descarta endometriosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"123","text":"Impacto salud mental es PARTE DE LA ENFERMEDAD → tamizar siempre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"123","text":"DIU-LNG → opción subestimada, eficaz en dismenorrea y adenomiosis coexistente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"123","text":"En contexto ICSI → endometriosis no contraindica, tasas similares otras causas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"1. Young SL. Nonsurgical approaches to the diagnosis and evaluation of endometriosis. Fertil Steril. 2023;121(2):140-144. DOI: 10.1016/j.fertnstert.2023.12.020","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"2. Donnez J, Stratopoulou CA, Dolmans MM. Endometriosis and adenomyosis: Similarities and differences. Best Pract Res Clin Obstet Gynaecol. 2023;92:102432. DOI: 10.1016/j.bpobgyn.2023.102432","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"3. Zippl AL, Reiser E, Seeber B. Endometriosis and mental health disorders. Fertil Steril. 2023;121(3):370-378. DOI: 10.1016/j.fertnstert.2023.12.033","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"132","text":"4. Veth VB et al. Recurrence after surgery for endometrioma: systematic review and meta-analyses. Fertil Steril. 2024;122(6):1079-1093. DOI: 10.1016/j.fertnstert.2024.07.033","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":136,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Obstetricia y Ginecología","filename":"Endometriosis iPad","id":"map_1476","resolved_references":[]}